  <h2 class="mt-5">Datasets</h2>
  <p>Research datasets for academic and educational purposes.</p>

  <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-database me-2 text-dark"></i>WikiFirst</h5>
          <p class="card-text">A corpus for investigating the impact of content variation on authorship similarity under a fixed genre. Consists exclusively of first revisions authored by non-anonymous Wikipedia editors.</p>
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.34740/kaggle/dsv/14818305" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm me-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download Dataset</a>
